2️⃣ Browser Troubleshooting Workflow
User symptom: “Websites won’t load” or “Chrome keeps spinning.”

🧩 Step-by-step workflow
Check DNS resolution

If DNS fails → browser won’t load anything

Test internet connectivity

Ping 8.8.8.8

Ping website domain

Check proxy settings

Incorrect proxy = instant browser failure

Check browser cache size

Large or corrupted cache slows everything

Test in Incognito mode

If it works → extension or profile issue

Disable extensions

Ad blockers and password managers often break pages

Check default browser settings

Wrong associations cause links to fail

🎯 Resolution examples
Clear cache

Reset Chrome profile

Disable problematic extensions

Fix proxy settings
